### Book a visitor slot
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visitorId": "visitor-uuid-here",
  "slotId": "slot-uuid-here",
  "bookingDate": "2024-11-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "numberOfPeople": 3,
  "specialRequests": "Wheelchair accessible entrance required",
  "notes": "First time visitor"
}

### Get visitor slot by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/booking-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Get all visitor slots with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot?status=booked&numberOfPeopleMin=2&numberOfPeopleMax=5
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Get visitor slots by visitor ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/visitor/visitor-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Get visitor slots by slot ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/slot/slot-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Check slot availability
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/availability/slot-uuid-here/2024-11-20
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Update visitor slot booking
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/booking-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "numberOfPeople": 4,
  "specialRequests": "Updated: Wheelchair accessible entrance and audio guide required",
  "notes": "Updated booking details"
}

### Cancel visitor slot booking
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/booking-uuid-here/cancel
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Delete visitor slot booking
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/booking-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Get visitor slot statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/stats
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Book visitor slot with minimal data
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visitorId": "visitor-uuid-here",
  "slotId": "slot-uuid-here",
  "bookingDate": "2024-11-21T00:00:00.000Z",
