}

### Book visitor slot with invalid data (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visitorId": "invalid-uuid",
  "slotId": "slot-uuid-here",
  "bookingDate": "2024-11-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "numberOfPeople": 0
}

### Search visitor slots by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot?bookingDateFrom=2024-11-01T00:00:00.000Z&bookingDateTo=2024-11-30T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Search visitor slots by status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/visitor-slot?status=cancelled
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here
